This directory contains some AmigaOS specific files.

Copy rapidoc2html, rapidoc2pdf, rapidoc2printer batch files to S: and ensure
that protection bits are set to RWEDS.

Copy rapidoc.r to S:

rapidoc2html converts a given rapidoc document file to a structured html file.

rapidoc2pdf converts a given rapidoc document file to a PFD1.3 document.

rapidoc2printer prints a rapidoc document (needs TurboPrint 7 full version).


Additionally you can install the file type definitions for Opus Magellan Desktop:

Copy Opus/Filetypes/Rapidoc Document (English descriptions) or
     Opus/Filetypes/Rapidoc Dokument (German descriptions) to DOpus5:Filetypes/


